{"tid":584553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑人電影《黑豹》香港大賣座, 票房邁向6000萬","createTime":"2018-03-08T01:46:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T10:51:18.000Z","uid":134071,"like":9,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"4cf806ffcf65648e9fb9ae49af111f6eab720c16","tid":584553,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T01:46:28.000Z","msg":"黑人電影係香港咁賣座, 做賀歲票房冠軍, 票房邁向6000萬, 都算係破天荒.   <br />\n<br />\n記得黑人明星Denzel Washington同Will Smith主演既電影係香港都唔太收得. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/60073\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Farchives%2F60073&d=ONgFi9cXp6Cz2mWfo5L8sCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=da0aa45b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/60073</a><br />\n<br />\n仍在上映電影方面，迪士尼發行的超級英雄電影《黑豹》踏入第三個周末獲增場一成三後，昨於51院平均各映四場錄得逾萬八飣人，每場平均人次仍達72，推算收入在百四萬以上，可算是口碑帶動，觀乎目前距離六千萬大關只差約130萬，相信本周達標。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/08/094614_a017e0caf9119cc47e6729799c0161ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F08%2F094614_a017e0caf9119cc47e6729799c0161ba.jpg&h=ee3359d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3822f320c2913ae7c88166de3f5d52bdc56f278b","tid":584553,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T01:59:49.000Z","msg":"19 表示左膠霸權<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cbcbff2ce4e89dfd54b93ceaee0c82b0c2961e5","tid":584553,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T02:02:26.000Z","msg":"海報影到個妹咁樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a274fcfa6afb73aff0a92f586deec781c609bfd4","tid":584553,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3822f320c2913ae7c88166de3f5d52bdc56f278b","tid":584553,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T01:59:49.000Z","msg":"19 表示左膠霸權<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/3